<article>
  <h2>about me</h2>
{% snippet %}

Among other [things](https://williamwhitaker.art), I'm a front-end developer. My focus is the space where visual design, accessible content, and code meet.  
&#8287;  

I create delightful experiences for users that help individuals and organizaions communicate with their audiences, whoever and wherever they may be.

